{"tid":2009653,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"察覺唔少火影撚下意息反抗博人傳","createTime":"2020-05-10T02:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T01:54:39.000Z","uid":57911,"like":6,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2a9d60c2d9828a2ba951910285e020388fde5ad9","tid":2009653,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T02:06:39.000Z","msg":"作為火影撚應該要勇於接受作品嘅好與壞<br />\n博人傳作為續集<br />\n願意為你啲舊電池出套過去篇<br />\n又俾博仔同寧次有超時空互動<br />\n證明火影套作品係冇放棄到寧次<br />\n連官方都冇放棄一個死得好慘嘅角色<br />\n點解火影撚要四處負皮博人傳<br />\n我哋應該要學識接受作品嘅全部先係<br />\n去到依度我哋要相信官方會願意幫忍術博士埋尾<br />\n令我大三代火影重回忍術博士嘅榮耀"},{"pid":"12976a08d8a35292fb0d4d869b44286e98737314","tid":2009653,"uid":306676,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T02:08:56.000Z","msg":"火影忍者比狗睇"},{"pid":"546e4e532bfd1501b22b6e46b00d0e9794d9cde6","tid":2009653,"uid":57911,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T02:09:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OuS6s3x.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOuS6s3x.gif&h=72d7f80a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0687d473656a4f0d35cbd29a001d5367810f0023","tid":2009653,"uid":62167,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T02:13:47.000Z","msg":"點都好都冇時間再睇 一定拖到仆街"},{"pid":"6cc3dc9f28d5f7dc612fa09ddf7b9e907d0842a6","tid":2009653,"uid":82889,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"12976a08d8a35292fb0d4d869b44286e98737314","tid":2009653,"uid":306676,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T02:08:56.000Z","msg":"火影忍者比狗睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:01:11.000Z","msg":"睇火影既係狗 唔睇火影既人狗都不如"},{"pid":"d34828c5e590f2ed70ba1b27757fe20b449d42cd","tid":2009653,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6cc3dc9f28d5f7dc612fa09ddf7b9e907d0842a6","tid":2009653,"uid":82889,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"12976a08d8a35292fb0d4d869b44286e98737314","tid":2009653,"uid":306676,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT